MANDATORY format for `rationale`: one sentence (max 15 words), then `\n- ` bullets (max 10 words each). No plain-text paragraphs.

Good: `"This fix-and-rerun cycle appeared often in your sessions.\n- Automating it saves many rounds of back-and-forth\n- The steps are consistent enough to reuse"`
Bad: `"Based on the analysis, this pattern happens frequently and would benefit from automation."`
